               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310217-235-person2191">
                  WILLIAM 
                  SMITH
               <interp inst="t18310217-235-person2191" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310217-235-person2191" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310217-235-person2191" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker, and live in Lower-street, Islington. On the evening of the 20th of January, the prisoner brought this plough plane to pawn; I questioned him - he said he was sent to pawn it by a person named Smith, in Paradise-row; I told him to fetch the man - he went away, returned, and said the person was very busy - he could not come that night, and I must give him the plane again; I said the person might come in the morning - I detained the plane; he went away, and did not return.</p>
               <p>
            
