            . I am a <rs id="t18310217-235-viclabel1376" type="occupation">carpenter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-235-victim2188 t18310217-235-viclabel1376"></join>, and live in Brooksby-street, Islington. This plane is mine, and was lost from my shop in <placeName id="t18310217-235-crimeloc1377">Barford-buildings, Liverpool-road</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310217-235-crimeloc1377" type="placeName" value="Barford-buildings, Liverpool-road"></interp>
