               <p>WILLIAM CARTWRIGHT. I keep a broker's shop. I bought this smoothing plane, on or about the 20th of January, of a boy, who I believe was the prisoner.</p>
               <p>WILLIAM RICHARDSON. I am <rs id="t18310217-235-viclabel1378" type="occupation">foreman</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-235-victim2190 t18310217-235-viclabel1378"></join> to Mr. Featham. This plane is mine - I did not miss it till I was informed where it was; the prisoner's father works near our premises, and I have seen the prisoner come backwards and forwards very frequently - this plane might have been gone a week before I missed it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310217-235-person2193">
